@Node Main "fREQ V2.5 Manual"

	fREQ V2.5
	=========

A filerequest manager for every fidonet user!

	Copyright 1995-96 Stefano Cairoli

	@{"Introduction" link "Introduction"}

	@{"Installation" link "Installation"}
	@{"Usage" link "Usage"}

	@{"History" link "History"}
